list.name: Message
list.query: SELECT title,tags,text FROM flightdata.events WHERE $timeFilter AND "event_type"='msg'

list.query: SELECT title,tags,text FROM flightdata.events WHERE $timeFilter AND "event_type"='ev'

list.name: Error

targets.query: SELECT mean(Roll) - mean(DesRoll) AS diff FROM "flight_att" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean(Pitch) - mean(DesPitch) AS diff FROM "flight_att" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean(Yaw) - mean(DesYaw) AS diff FROM "flight_att" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT "HDop" FROM "flight_gps" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s) fill(none)
SELECT mean(ThI) - mean(ThO) AS diff FROM "flight_ctun" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean(CRt) - mean(DCRt) AS diff FROM "flight_ctun" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
